1. "*Sin* je prouzrokovao veliku štetu" (The sin caused great damage)
2. "*Sin* je velika stvar koja se ne može zanemariti" (Sin is a big thing that can not be ignored)
3. "*Sinov*e često imaju teškoće u vezi sa roditeljima" (Sons often have difficulties with parents)
4. "On je bio *sinska* osoba" (He was a sinful person)
5. "Ona je bila *sinovska* prema njenom bratu" (She was sisterly towards her brother)